translations: n.[冶][化工]萃取器；提取者；采掘性企业（extractor 的复数）

sentences.sentence: Deflated values also mean that natural gas extractors see no reason to capture helium.
sentences.translation: 放气值也意味着天然气提取器认为没有捕获氦的需要。

sentences.sentence: Foreign resource extractors are queuing up.
sentences.translation: 国外资源提炼公司也在排着队。

sentences.sentence: Regexes in Scala translate those capture groups to extractors.
sentences.translation: Scala的正则表达式会把这些捕捉组翻译成抽取器。
